{"tid":1792918,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"金正恩: 將做到「時代」同「革命」所賦予的神聖使命及任務","createTime":"2019-12-22T04:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T06:38:39.000Z","uid":273852,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"43e73c5e7b1e47c7b6b4ac091f2b22adafdbbf31","tid":1792918,"uid":273852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:14:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20191222/mobile/bkn-20191222083301375-1222_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20191222%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191222083301375-1222_00912_001.html&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3NUqyFx8t7fe88%2BQEXu6%2F%2FM%3D&h=77205825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20191222/mobile/bkn-20191222083301375-1222_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n距離美朝無核化談判死線不足兩周之際，北韓領袖金正恩主持勞動黨中央軍事委員會擴大會議。他以國內外形勢複雜為由，下令進一步加強人民軍，並繼續改進及快速發展自衞的國防力量，以及根據軍事戰略，重新組建、擴大及改組軍事部隊。<br />\n朝中社周日（22日）報道，與會者屬於各級武力機關指揮成員，來自勞動黨中央軍事委員會委員、人民軍各軍種及軍級指揮員、總政治局、總參謀部、人民武裝力量省指揮成員、人民保安省、國家保衞省、護衞司令部。金正恩說，要順應形勢變化潮流及北韓革命發展關鍵時期的要求，從軍事政治層面進一步加強全國武裝力量。<br />\n<br />\n會議也討論及決定要更切實保證及實現，勞動黨領導國家的「全盤武裝力量」，並分析人民軍各級單位和部門的工作情況，同時指出不合理機構、編制和在其他軍事政治活動出現的一系列缺點；會議又罷免和補選部分勞動黨中央軍事委員會委員。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩在會上指出，近期在人民軍工作出現的優缺點和要盡快克服的問題，並具體指明今後軍隊建設和軍事政治活動的方向及途徑；又稱期待及相信所有指揮人員，將做到時代和革命所賦予的神聖使命及任務。惟報道沒有提及美朝談判死線一事。"},{"pid":"9e231c9ab53caf083d57065003eddfd447044176","tid":1792918,"uid":49018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zjT1qE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zjT1qE.jpg&h=f1f65c75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日三點半，麻煩大家準時！<br />\n現場唔好有連豬，連狗<br />\n尊重返人哋啲宗教<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAHBZcu.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAHBZcu.gif&h=f5f36c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zpRGqSx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzpRGqSx.gif&h=bc12f105&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，&Ouml;zil畀人屌到屎眼爛都冇跪<br />\n我哋聽日都要支持佢<br />\n<br />\nStand with Uyghur(We ga）, Stand with &Ouml;zil（奧燒）"},{"pid":"e7e405080340427837877a55fb12c1949eb62b61","tid":1792918,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:15:30.000Z","msg":"反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7429ad74440ec874b130cc66ba33822c7781f2c","tid":1792918,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:18:34.000Z","msg":"南有香港<br />\n東有朝鮮<br />\n西有突厥<br />\n北有俄國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34cd5106409fe9157ce75bc06c6888499cfd0762","tid":1792918,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c56585aa32398682df8439d4473503183ca5de","tid":1792918,"uid":191812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5936625336eaa4c6fa7648ad2da9f2c1d5f311fe","tid":1792918,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:21:10.000Z","msg":"光韓北韓 時代革命<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c7249b317ae8274ec6cc51b78f01acfc025dac","tid":1792918,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:23:32.000Z","msg":"火箭人都作反<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6b0de4113079b9b47951852c9a17c6cedcfba6","tid":1792918,"uid":315761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci